title: Instant Reactions to the Carson Wentz Trade
description:
Nora Princiotti is joined by The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz to discuss the Philadelphia Eagles trading Carson Wentz to the Indianapolis Colts. Then they talk about which quarterback they think could be on the move next.

Host: Nora Princiotti
Guest: Danny Heifetz
